    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable car for me and is still in really solid shape! It drives smoothly, looks great, and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the basics so you can just hop in and go. Perfect for someone looking for a dependable daily driver without breaking the bank. Drop me a message\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
