    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride of ownership, offering a seamless blend of performance and everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, complemented by well-preserved alloy wheels. While there are a few minor, unavoidable stone chips on the front fascia from highway use, the body remains straight and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the seats show only light softening of the bolsters, and the dashboard remains free of any UV damage or cracks. All electronic features, from the premium audio system to the dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having recently undergone a comprehensive inspection and oil service. The engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the transmission shifts with factory-like precision. It comes with a folder of service records, a clean title, and the peace of mind that it has been cared for by a truly detail-oriented owner.",
